wallbox v0.1

WARNING: this project only has pre-alpha quality.
design document:

http://docs.google.com/View?id=ajd93zkqrjq5_342cqdrxqcd

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Prerequisites
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

In Ubuntu 9.04 (Karmic), python-facebook is too old.
please install python-facebook 0.svn20090724-1.1 from lucid.

http://packages.ubuntu.com/lucid/all/python-facebook/download

In Debian Squeeze/Sid please install python-facebook:
# apt-get install python-facebook

In Arch Linux please install pyfacebook-git from AUR.
$ yaourt -S pyfacebook-git


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Run
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

$ cd src/wallbox
$ ./wallbox.py


